<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zgh" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Tasleḍt n tmuɣli — Terroir.ma</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Tifinagh', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2e7d32;">Tmuɣli ttwasleḍt</h1>

  <p>Aselway,</p>

  <p>
    Nefraḥ ad ak-nessiwel belli tmuɣli-nnek <strong>ttwaqbilt d ttwasleḍt</strong>
    ɣef usebter Terroir.ma. Tzemreḍ tura ad tseqdceḍ akk iferdisen n usentem.
  </p>

  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Isem n tmuɣli</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{cooperativeName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Unumro n useɣ</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{cooperativeNumber}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Azemz n tasleḍt</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{verifiedAt}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top: 32px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">
    Iyawalen-a ttwaznen s wudem awurman seg usebter Terroir.ma.<br>
    Ur d-trarreḍ ɣef yiyawalen-a.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
